      <h1><span class="position">#253</span> CarrierWave File Uploads</h1>
      <div class="details">Feb 14, 2011 | 9 minutes | <a href="/?tag_id=13">Plugins</a></div>
      <div class="description">CarrierWave makes it easy and clean to add file uploads to your application. It supports a variety of ORMs, frameworks and image processors.</div>
